* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/ˈæb.sə.ˌlu.ˌtɪz.əm/}}
* {{audio|en-us-absolutism.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{context|political science}} The principles or practice of absolute or arbitrary government; [[despotism]].
#:* The element of ''absolutism'' and prelacy was controlling. - [[Palfrey]]
# {{context|theology}} Doctrine of absolute decrees. - [[Ash]]
# The state of being absolute; the system or doctrine of the absolute;

